				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Isaiah 44:24</p>\n<p>'Thus says the Lord, your Redeemer, who formed you from the womb: “I am the Lord, who made all things, who alone stretched out the heavens, who spread out the earth by myself'</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://my.bible.com/en-GB/bible/59/ISA.44.24\"><img title=\"135944738_3722faab30_b.jpg\" src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/80d3e6a4cf.jpg\" alt=\"135944738 3722faab30 b\" width=\"976\" height=\"1024\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T20:17:50+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/isaiah-thus-says.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/194027.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>1 Corinthians 10:17</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/1co.10.17.ESV\"><img src=\"uploads/2022/30643bd29c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:40:27+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/194027.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193929.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Genesis 1:1-2</p>\n<p>When I first came to Christ and really started to read and appreciate the Word of God properly I think it was the first two lines that made me realise that The Bible really was inspired. So few words but never more profound. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/gen.1.1-2.ESV\"><img src=\"uploads/2022/c54f7e9929.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:39:29+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193929.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193913.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Acts 13:41</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/act.13.41.ESV\"><img src=\"uploads/2022/0845e65f71.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:39:13+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193913.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193854.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Acts 17:30-31</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/act.17.30-31.ESV\"><img src=\"uploads/2022/f048a7392d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:38:54+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193854.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193801.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Acts 19:2</p>\n<p>And they say there is no evidence of The Trinity in the early Church.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/act.19.2.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/6062e78ab4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:38:01+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193801.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193741.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p> </p>\n<p>Acts 19:11-12. Paul heals in Ephesus.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/act.19.11-12.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/abad7ae90e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:37:41+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193741.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193726.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Jeremiah 17:8</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/jer.17.8.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/d9152607bc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:37:26+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193726.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193711.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Acts 26:10. If a soul like Saul's can be saved, our salvation is secure!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/act.26.10.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/f0af5d768c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:37:11+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193711.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193656.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Romans 12:2</p>\n<p>Be transformed by the renewal of your mind.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/rom.12.2.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/148ee1f809.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:36:56+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193656.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193642.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Romans 3:23-24</p>\n<p>For all have sinned and fallen short of the glory of God.</p>\n<p>Yet Jesus Saves</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/rom.3.23-24.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/4dcd1728c9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:36:42+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193642.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/isaiahbible.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Isaiah 5:22.</p>\n<p>Woe to those who are heroes at drinking wine and champions at mixing drinks.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://isaiah.bible/isaiah-5-22\"><img src=\"uploads/2022/630415d5ba.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:36:26+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/isaiahbible.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193612.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Romans 6:23. The wages of sin is death.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://romans.bible/romans-6-23\"><img src=\"uploads/2022/1949934aa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:36:12+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193612.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193556.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Romans 8:26</p>\n<p>When we cannot find the words, the Spirit will ensure the Father understands.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/rom.8.26.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/acc3bf3594.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:35:56+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193556.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193541.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Matthew 7:8 For everyone who asks receives.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/mat.7.8.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/be4dc894f2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:35:41+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193541.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193529.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Romans 12:14 Bless those who persecute you.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/rom.12.14.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/6607b94167.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:35:29+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193529.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193515.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Romans 11:36</p>\n<p>Since all things are from God, and through God, and for God, it follows that He deserves all the glory forever (ESV Study Bible).</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/rom.11.36.ESV\"><img src=\"uploads/2022/ceefd65dcc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:35:15+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193515.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193501.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Colossians 3:23</p>\n<p>Do what you do for the glory of God, not the approval of men.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/12/col.3.23.ASV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/fd0ef8fd81.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:35:01+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193501.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193447.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p> </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/rom.13.1.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/2dac07eb3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:34:47+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193447.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/romansbible.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Romans 14:1. Let us not divide over secondary issues!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://romans.bible/romans-14-1\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/7b02954d06.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:34:32+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/romansbible.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193414.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Psalm 69:4 Mighty are those who would destroy me.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/psa.69.4.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/95a991bbb1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:34:14+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193414.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193359.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Hebrews 4:15 Jesus, our High Priest - who knows what it is to be man, yet did not sin.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/heb.4.15.ESV\"><img src=\"uploads/2022/7e50fb15c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:33:59+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193359.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193340.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Hebrews 7:26-27</p>\n<p>Jesus Saves. He has no need to offer sacrifices daily since he did this once for all.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/heb.7.26-27.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/1bc6447a5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:33:40+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193340.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193326.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Daniel 10:12.</p>\n<p>God speaks to the humble, gives them encouragement and understanding.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/dan.10.12.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/dc084bc583.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:33:26+01:00",
				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193326.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193311.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Psalm 126:6</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/psa.126.6.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/0a448c47da.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:33:11+01:00",
