				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193223.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193209.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Sometimes, that 'hot-take' might not be so wise. James 1:19</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible.com/bible/59/jas.1.19.ESV\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/37bed32f87.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
				"date_published": "2022-08-03T19:32:09+01:00",
