				"url": "https://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/193138.html",
				"tags": ["Verse of the Day"]
			},
			{
				"id": "http://weneedanark.micro.blog/2022/08/03/revelationbible.html",
				
				"content_html": "<!-- raw HTML omitted -->\n",
				"content_text": "<p>Revelation 7:17 And God will wipe away every tear from their eyes.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://revelation.bible/revelation-7-17\"><img src=\"https://weneedanark.micro.blog/uploads/2022/16c1a2f8d0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n",
